<gco:CharacterString>Entity and Attribute Overview: Aquatic Recreation Use Support Assessments - 2004 Entity and Attribute Detail Citation: AUID = Assessment Unit ID is the MN Department of Natural Resources Public Waters Inventory number which is formatted CC-LLLL-BB. CC is the two digit county number, LLLL is the four digit lake number (unique within county) and BB is the two digit bay number (00 if the id represents the entire lake). ENTITY_ID = A Waterbody Identifier that is the two letter state abbreviation MN concatenated with the AUID. This ID format is transmitted to EPA for reporting purposes. WATER_NAME = Waterbody name from 1:24,000 scale USGS quandrangle maps. ASSESSMENT = Level of use support for Aquatic Recreation Fully Supporting Partially Supporting Not Supporting ACRES = Waterbody size based on MN Department of Natural Resources Bulletin 25.</gco:CharacterString>                </gmd:otherCitationDetails>             </gmd:CI_Citation>          </gmd:featureCatalogueCitation>       </gmd:MD_FeatureCatalogueDescription>
